{"parse":{"title":"Scarlet Monastery","pageid":327900,"wikitext":{"*":"{{lookingfor|the old instance of the same name called [[Scarlet Monastery (original)|Scarlet Monastery]]}}\n{{Mists-article}}\n{{infobox instance\n|name=Scarlet Monastery\n|aka=SC, SM - c, SM - g\n|ss=\n|caption=Scarlet Monastery loading graphic\n|loc=[[Whispering Gardens]], [[Tirisfal Glades]] \n|race={{Race|Human}}<br />{{Race|Undead}}\n|boss={{mob|boss=|High Inquisitor Whitemane}} (Cathedral)<br/>{{mob|boss=|Thalnos the Soulrender}} (Graveyard)\n|type=Low-level normal, Heroic\n|level=Graveyard: 30-32{{fact}}, 90<br/>Cathedral: 32-33{{fact}}, 90\n|minlevel=23 (28), 90\n|players=5\n|key=\n|bosses={{Scarlet Monastery}}\n}}\n'''Scarlet Monastery''' (also known as \"Scarlet Cathedral\") is a revamped dungeon in the new expansion, {{Mists-inline}} [[Mists of Pandaria]]. It is basically just redone versions of the Graveyard and Cathedral areas in one wing. The old Armory and Library areas have been combined into another wing called [[Scarlet Halls]].\n\nThe Scarlet Cathedral is the dungeon wing (level 21+ and level 90) of the re-introduced Scarlet Monastery in the {{mists-inline}} Mists of Pandaria expansion. It replaces what were previously two wings, the \"[[Scarlet_Monastery_(original)#Graveyard_.2826.2B.29|Graveyard]]\" and the \"[[Scarlet_Monastery_(original)#Cathedral_.2835.2B.29|Cathedral]].\"\n\n\n== New in Mists of Pandaria ==\n{{mists-section}}\nDuring [[Blizzcon 2011]], it was announced that level 90, Heroic version of this dungeon would be available for the upcoming expansion {{mists-inline}} Mists of Pandaria.{{fact}} Also, the dungeon will be revamped from 4 wings to 2 wings with several different bosses.<ref>{{ref web|work=[[WoW Insider]]|url=http://wow.joystiq.com/2012/04/08/mists-of-pandaria-beta-scarlet-monastery-revamp/|title=Mists of Pandaria Beta: Scarlet Monastery revamp|author={{wowinsider|Megan ONeill|Megan O'Neill}}|date=8-Apr-2012 6:00PM}}</ref>\n\n== Story ==\nThe '''Scarlet Monastery''' is one of four strongholds in the world belonging to the fanatical [[Scarlet Crusade]], the others being the [[Scarlet Bastion]] within the ruins of [[Stratholme]], the [[town]] of [[Hearthglen]], and the town of [[Tyr's Hand]].  Located in the northeast corner of the blighted [[Tirisfal Glades]], the Scarlet Monastery was once a cathedral to the [[Light]], now taken over by zealots. The Scarlet Monastery is a complex of four wings, each an [[instance]]d dungeon, for both Horde and Alliance characters. The mobs respawn at the same rate in each of them, except for the Cathedral.\n\nAll of the instanced wings of the Scarlet Monastery are stored on the same map. That means, if you could fly, you can enter the Cathedral, fly, and end up in the Graveyard wing.\n\n== History ==\n{{wow-dungeons}}\n:''The Monastery was once a proud bastion of Lordaeron's priesthood - a center for learning and enlightenment.  With the rise of the undead [[Scourge]] during the [[Third War]], the peaceful Monastery was converted into a stronghold of the fanatical Scarlet Crusade.  The Crusaders are intolerant of all non-human races, regardless of alliance or affiliation.  They believe that any and all outsiders are potential carriers of the undead plague - and must be destroyed.  Reports indicate that adventurers who enter the monastery are forced to contend with [[Scarlet Commander Mograine]] - who commands a large garrison of fanatically devoted warriors.  However, the monastery's true master is [[High Inquisitor Whitemane]] - a fearsome priestess who possesses the ability to resurrect fallen warriors to do battle in her name.''\n\n== Loot ==\n{{Sectionstub/Generic|type=Location}}\n\n== Mobs ==\n{{Sectionstub/Generic|type=Location}}\n\n== Bosses ==\n{{Sectionstub/Generic|type=Location}}\n\n== Maps ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nFile:WorldMap-ScarletCathedral1.jpg|Graveyard\nFile:WorldMap-ScarletCathedral2.jpg|Cathedral\n</gallery>\n\n== Achievements ==\n{{sectionstub}}\n\n== Quest guide ==\n{{sectionstub}}\n\n{| class=\"darktable\"\n|+ Quests\n|-\n! Faction\n! Quest name\n! Quest giver\n! Zone location\n! Significant areas\n|-\n!rowspan=\"1\"|{{Horde}} Horde\n| {{questlong|Horde|90 <small>Daily Heroic</small>|A Worthy Challenge: Durand}}\n| {{RaceIcon|Pandaren|Male|Small}}{{NPC|Horde|Challenger Wuli}}\n| [[Shrine of Two Moons]], [[Vale of Eternal Blossoms]], [[Pandaria]]\n| Cathedral\n|- \t\n!rowspan=\"1\"|{{Alliance}} Alliance\n| {{questlong|Alliance|90 <small>Daily Heroic</small>|A Worthy Challenge: Durand}}\n| {{RaceIcon|Pandaren|Male|Small}}{{NPC|Alliance|Challenger Soong }}\n| [[Shrine of Seven Stars]], [[Vale of Eternal Blossoms]], [[Pandaria]]\n| Cathedral\n|}\n\n== Areas ==\n[[File:Scarlet Monastery Location.jpg|thumb|right|Scarlet Monastery location on the map of Tirisfal Glades.]]\n\n=== Graveyard (30+) ===\n{{sectionstub}}\n\n=== Cathedral (32+) ===\n[[File:Scarlet Monastery.jpg|thumb|The Cathedral of the Scarlet Monastery.]]\n{{sectionstub}}\n\n== Dungeon denizens ==\n{{main|Scarlet Monastery mobs}}\n{{sectionstub}}\n<!--\n* {{RaceIconExt|Fire|Small}} [[Fire elemental]]s\n* {{RaceIcon|Undead|Male|Small}}{{RaceIcon|Undead|Female|Small}} [[Forsaken]]\n* {{RaceIconExt|Ghost|Small}} [[Ghost]] (one, [[Azshir the Sleepless]])\n* {{RaceIcon|Human|Male|Small}}{{RaceIcon|Human|Female|Small}} [[Human]]s\n* {{RaceIconExt|Hyena|Small}} [[Hyena]]s\n* {{RaceIconExt|Rabbit|Small}} [[Rabbit]]s (critters)\n* {{RaceIconExt|Rat|Small}} [[Rat]]s (critters)\n* {{RaceIconExt|Shade|Small}} [[Shade]]s\n* {{RaceIconExt|SkeletalMage|Small}} [[Skeletal mage]] (one, [[Bloodmage Thalnos]])\n* {{RaceIconExt|SkeletalWarrior|Small}} [[Skeletal warrior]] (one, [[Ironspine]])\n* {{RaceIconExt|Wraith|Small}} [[Wraith]]s\n* {{RaceIconExt|Zombie|Small}} [[Zombie]]s\n-->\n\n== Loot ==\n{{sectionstub}}\n\n{| class=\"darktable zebra\"\n|+ Loot\n|-\n!Boss\n!Instance\n!Weapons and Shields\n!Cloth\n!Leather\n!Mail\n!Plate\n!Back\n!Other\n<!--\n|- \n|{{mob|Azshir the Sleepless}} ''(Rare)''\n|Graveyard\n|\n{{loot|Rare|Necrotic Wand}}\n|\n{{loot|Rare|Blighted Leggings}}\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n{{loot|Rare|Ghostshard Talisman}}\n-->\n|}\n\n== Resources ==\n{{sectionstub}}\n\n== Media ==\n=== Videos ===\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\">\nFile:Scarlet Monastery Revamp - Mists of Pandaria Beta\n</gallery>\n\n== Patch changes ==\n* {{Patch 5.0.4|note=Level range adjusted. Cut down to 2 areas in 1 wing from 4 wings. Heroic mode added.}}\n* {{Patch 4.0.3a|note=Level range adjusted.}}\n* {{Patch 3.0.2|note=NPCs no longer bow to a player with {{loot|Epic|Corrupted Ashbringer}}.}}\n* {{Patch 2.3.0|note=Loot from all bosses greatly improved.}}\n* {{Patch 1.3.0|note=\n**Capped at ten players.\n**Doors requiring the Scarlet Key can now also be opened with a Large Seaforium Charge in addition to the lockpick ability.}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}} \n\n== See also ==\n* [[Scarlet Halls]]\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{bnetwowinstance|Scarlet Monastery}}\n{{elinks-zone|6109}}\n\n;Guides\n{{elink|icon=icyveinscom|site=Icy Veins|link=http://www.icy-veins.com/scarlet-monastery-wow-heroic-dungeon-guide|desc=Scarlet Monastery Walkthrough (Bosses, Achievements, Loot, and Quests)}}\n\n;Lore\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2012/01/22/know-your-lore-scarlet-monastery-revisited/|desc=Know Your Lore: Scarlet Monastery revisited|bydate=by {{wowinsider|Anne Stickney}} Jan 22nd 2012 at 4:00PM}}\n\n;News\n{{elink|type=wowheadnews|link=http://www.wowhead.com/news=204817/mists-of-pandaria-loot-tables-and-dungeon-journals|desc=Mists of Pandaria Loot Tables and Dungeon Journals|bydate=by [http://www.wowhead.com/news&user=Ashelia Ashelia] 2012/07/18 1:52 PM}}\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2012/04/08/mists-of-pandaria-beta-scarlet-monastery-revamp/|desc=Mists of Pandaria Beta: Scarlet Monastery revamp|bydate=by {{wowinsider|Megan ONeill|Megan O'Neill}} Apr 8th 2012 6:00PM}}\n{{elink|type=wowheadnews|link=http://www.wowhead.com/news=201965/mists-of-pandaria-preview-the-scarlet-halls-and-cathedral-redesigns|desc=Mists of Pandaria Preview: The Scarlet Halls and Cathedral Redesigns|bydate=by [http://www.wowhead.com/news&user=Ashelia Ashelia] 2012/03/24 at 9:01 AM}}\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2012/03/19/mists-of-pandaria-dungeon-preview/|desc=Mists of Pandaria: Dungeons and challenge mode|bydate=by {{wowinsider|Alex Ziebart}} Mar 19th 2012 3:01AM}}\n\n\n{{Scarlet Monastery Subzones}}\n{{Tirisfal Glades}}\n{{Dungeons}}\n\n[[de:Scharlachrotes Kloster]]\n[[es:Scarlet Monastery]]\n[[pl:Scarlet Monastery]]\n[[ru:\u041c\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044b\u0440\u044c \u0410\u043b\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043e\u0440\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0430]]"}}}